column167: participantComments:"I thought the directions were convoluted & over-complicated. Sorry... but true! The obvious answer (on a real farm) would be for each PacMan farmer to harvest ALL of the tree closest to them
column168: then meet in the middle - literally
column169: and metaphorically - to separate & swap their fruits into their preferred colors. Would have been more fun if there were options for the farmers to figure out something like this
column170: beyond the parameters of the game."
